data.name: lblDocTypes_Definition.Text
data.value: Document Types - A collection of documents classifications for documents parsed (analyzed) by the Document Analyzer and then their parsed segments/paragraphs allocated into a Matrix. For example, the Federal Government RFP sections (e.g. Section C Statement of Work).

data.name: lblRefResDescription.Text
data.value: A collection of reusable excerpts content that can be allocated into a Matrix, such as Win Themes & Discriminators. Reference Resources can be shared between Workgroup or desinated to they selected Workgroup.
